title: Spyder Auto Installation: 2011-13 Jeep Grand Cherokee Step Bars
description: This video demonstrates how to install a set of Spyder Auto Step Bars on 2011-13 model Jeep Grand Cherokee SUVs. This complete walkthrough shows you everything you need to know, from what tools to use to where the brackets mount and is filled with helpful tips throughout to facilitate a successful installation.
